section Cylinder Cylinder models
state video on

caption .5 .15 3 A Cylinder has a specialized tool to edit the;\
    top and bottom diameters
state cursor on
state animation on
moveover CreateCylinderIcon 1
click
wait 3

caption .5 .15 4 Drag any handle to modify the diameter
moveover CylinderTool/TopRadiusScaler/MaxSlider 1
drag -.03 0 2

moveover CylinderTool/BottomRadiusScaler/MaxSlider 1 0 .009
drag .1 0 2

wait 3
